[DhtmlXQ_comment0]mg tactics discover check 02.||Using the cannon chariot discover checkmate technique.||This is game 018 of the Elegant Pastime Xq Manual. This is another example showing the use of the discover check. More often, the cannon is the piece performing the check. In this case, the chariot is performing the check. ||A simple anaysis of the board.||Black is one move away from a kill, R1+1/P3+1/P3=4/R7+7...||Red has the king cornered. The two black pawns at the riverbank are impeding the chariots from attack. And the cannons cannot perform any decent check...[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
